date.description: The date when the data was recorded

channel_id.description: The unique identifier for the YouTube channel

video_id.description: The unique identifier for the YouTube video

live_or_on_demand.description: Indicates whether the video was live or on-demand

subscribed_status.description: Indicates if the viewer was subscribed to the channel

country_code.description: The country code for the location targeted

end_screen_element_type.description: The type of end screen element (e.g., video, playlist, subscribe)

end_screen_element_id.description: The unique identifier for the end screen element

end_screen_element_clicks.description: The total number of clicks on end screen elements

end_screen_element_impressions.description: The total impressions of end screen elements

end_screen_element_click_rate.description: The rate at which viewers click on end screen elements
